org.dataconservancy.packaging.gui.util

Class ControlFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dataconservancy.packaging.gui.util.ControlFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CssConstants

    public class ControlFactory
extends Object
implements CssConstants
    A class to create Control objects for the Package Tool GUI. The main purpose of this is to provide resizing and tooltip functionality for various input controls.

      • createControl

        public static javafx.scene.control.Control createControl(ControlType type,
                                                         Object initialValue,
                                                         String helpText)
        This method creates various types of Controls for the GUI, setting various properties etc. as appropriate for the type of control created.
        Parameters:
        type - the ControlType of the control to be created
        initialValue - the initial text value for a text input control, ignored if not applicable
        helpText - the help text to display with the control
        Returns:
        the Control of the Type specified
